Reasoning: The paper deals with concepts related to lattices and domains, which are topics in theoretical computer science and logic. The use of Stone duality also suggests a connection to mathematical logic. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also involves some aspects of discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and programming languages (cs.PL), as well as information theory (cs.IT) and mathematical software (cs.MS).
